'''Kuchcel''' was a [[Governor/Legends|governor]] of an unknown [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. Kuchcel posted a bounty on [[Keezo Stoolee]] for destroying their millennium celebration. This bounty was eventually claimed by [[Jango Fett/Legends|Jango Fett]].

